author: @janjohnston2106
content:
Stupid...she is hobbling around on her legs..
After all sorts of falls onstage....and she doesn't see...mocking the truth....


Leaves her out in the cold....


Wealthy in this system....but what of the next....

Satan has a hold....but only a little while longer and he will not be there...

Psalms 83...18

Hallilujah
